    "title": {
        "rendered": "IDF spokesman update \u2013\u00a027.09, afternoon"
    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"\u05e2\u05d3\u05db\u05d5\u05df \u05d3\u05d5\u05d1\u05e8 \u05e6\u05d4&quot;\u05dc - 27.09, \u05e2\u05e8\u05d1\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/UTtJYTQG_sw?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Moments ago, as we head into Shabbat Shalom, the Israel Defense Forces carried out a precision strike.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">IDF Strike on Hezbollah&#8217;s Headquarters</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Israel Defense Forces carried out a precise strike on the central headquarters of the Hezbollah terror organization. This location served as the epicenter of Hezbollah&#8217;s terrorist activities.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Hezbollah&#8217;s Use of Human Shields</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hezbollah&#8217;s central headquarters was intentionally built under residential buildings in the heart of Beirut. This was part of Hezbollah&#8217;s strategy of using Lebanese civilians as human shields.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Hezbollah&#8217;s Aggression Against Israel</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>On October 8th, Hezbollah began attacking Israel after almost a year of firing rockets, missiles, and suicide drones at Israeli civilians.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Israel&#8217;s Response to Hezbollah&#8217;s Threat</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>For nearly a year, Israel warned the world, stating that Hezbollah must be stopped. Now, Israel is taking the necessary actions to protect its people, just as any sovereign state would if faced with a terror organization on its border.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ensuring Safety for Israeli Families</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Israel is acting so that Israeli families can leave their homes safely and securely.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Thank you.</p>\n",
        "protected": false
    },
    "excerpt": {
        "rendered": "<p>The IDF conducted a precision strike on <a  href=\"/hezbollah\">Hezbollah</a>&#8216;s headquarters in Beirut, responding to ongoing threats and aggression.</p>\n",
        "protected": false
    },
